membership:
CEFS is a founding member of: &#xd;
- the Primary Food Processors (PFP) created in 2009&#xd;
www.pfp-eu.org&#xd;
- Agriculture and Progress launched in 2018 with CIBE and CEPM&#xd;
CEFS is also member of:&#xd;
- FoodDrinkEurope (former CIAA: agro-food industries)&#xd;
- ADEA (Association of the Defence of the European Agriculture).&#xd;
https://www.eucofel.eu/adea&#xd;
&#xd;
CEFS launched in September 2015 the EU Beet sugar sustainability Partnership (EUBSSP) together with CIBE and EFFAT &#xd;
www.sustainablesugar.eu&#xd;
&#xd;
CEFS is also member of the EUBA: bioeconomy alliance

